# CSIでKubernetesと連携する方法



~~~
ceph auth get-or-create client.kubernetes mon 'profile rbd' osd 'profile rbd pool=blk_data' mgr 'profile rbd'
~~~




~~~
root@node1:~# ceph auth get-or-create client.kubernetes mon 'profile rbd' osd 'profile rbd pool=blk_data' mgr 'profile rbd'
[client.kubernetes]
	key = AQCNFtxeyHKhHBAAL6vZFQGF+JwofOadt2b3XA==
~~~


